source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_SEQ_00<tab>Papin wants to surprise his family with something nice.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_SEQ_00<tab>Papin est en admiration devant votre physique et aurait un service à vous demander.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_TODO_00<tab>Slay true griffins for their meat.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_TODO_00<tab>Abattre des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2164F0302 /var> pour obtenir leur viande

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the griffin meat to Papin.

TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_000<tab>Excuse me, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((mister)) /var>? I heard you adventurers are really brave, and strong. Do you think you can help me? I want to get Ma something real special, but I can't do it myself.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_000<tab>Woahh, t'as l'air super fort<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>... J'pourrais te demander de faire quelque chose d'un peu dangereux pour moi<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_001<tab>North of the village are these huge bird things called griffins, and their meat's supposed to be some of the best around.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_001<tab>Il y a des animaux monstrueux très puissants au nord d'ici. Ils sont tellement gros que nous on n'aurait aucune chance de les abattre, mais j'ai pourtant besoin de leur viande<var 1D /var>! Il m'en faut absolument<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_002<tab>If you could bring back even just a little, I'm sure it would make Ma awful happy to have it.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_002<tab>Tu veux bien être sympa et me ramener des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8DB50302 /var><var 1D /var>? S'il te plaît<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_003<tab>If you head up north, where all the soldiers used to be, there should be griffins around there. At least, that's what Ma says.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_003<tab>S'il te plaît. J'ai besoin de cette viande. Pour trouver <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F2164F0302 /var>, c'est facile, il suffit que t'ailles au nord d'ici<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_010<tab>My, that was fast. Did you see any griffins?
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_010<tab>Tu rapportes la viande que je t'ai demandée<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_011<tab>Wow, I didn't think you would bring back so much. You adventurers are really something else.

TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_012<tab>Have you ever had any before? Ma says this meat's supposed to be filled with all sorts of nutrients. Griffins are too dangerous to hunt, though, so we never get to eat any. Ma and Sis will be so happy.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_012<tab>Non seulement elle est délicieuse, mais en plus, ma mère m'a dit qu'il y avait plein de bonnes choses pour bien grandir dedans. On n'en mange vraiment pas souvent, je suis sûr que ma sœur sera contente aussi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_013<tab>A shame Pa isn't here to try it. He had to go away on work. He used to send me letters every day, but lately there's been nothing.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_013<tab>J'aurais voulu que papa puisse en manger aussi, mais il est parti loin à cause de son travail. Il n'envoie même plus de lettre maintenant. J'espère qu'il va vite revenir...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_014<tab>I'm sure he's okay. He's really strong, just like you. And when he comes back, we'll go hunting and have griffin meat all the time!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ902_02858_PAPIN_000_014<tab>En attendant, je vais m'entraîner pour devenir aussi fort que toi<var 1D /var>! Comme ça, je pourrai chasser, et on mangera de la viande à tous les repas<var 1D /var>! Merci, hein<var 1D /var>! N'hésite pas à repasser<var 1D /var>!
